side	1
of	1
its	1
path	1
round	1
the	1
sun,	1
or	1
185,000,000	1
miles	1
away	1
from	1
where	1
it	1
is	1
now.	1
Viewed	1
or	1
photographed	1
from	1
two	1
positions	1
so	1
wide	1
