nearest	1
star	1
to	1
the	1
earth,	1
a	1
recently	1
discovered	1
star,	1
is	1
twenty-five	1
trillion	1
miles	1
away.	1
Only	1
thirty	1
stars	1
are	1
known	1
to	1
be	1
within	1
a	1
hundred	1
trillion	1
miles	1
of	1
