THE	1
AURORA	1
BOREALIS	1
The	1
aurora	1
borealis	1
is	1
one	1
of	1
the	1
most	1
beautiful	1
spectacles	1
in	1
the	1
sky.	1
The	1
colours	1
and	1
shape	1
change	1
every	1
instant;	1
sometimes	1
a	1
fan-like	1
cluster	1
of	1
rays,	1
at	1
other	1
times	1
long	1
golden	1
draperies	1
gliding	1
one	1
over	1
the	1
other.	1
Blue,	1
green,	1
yellow,	1
red,	1
and	1
white	1
combine	1
to	1
give	1
a	1
glorious	1
display	1
of	1
colour.	1
The	1
theory	1
of	1
its	1
origin	1
is	1
still,	1
in	1
part,	1
obscure,	1
but	1
there	1
