from	1
outer	1
space,	1
and	1
has	1
been	1
burned	1
up	1
by	1
friction.	1
It	1
was	1
travelling	1
at,	1
perhaps,	1
twenty	1
or	1
thirty	1
miles	1
a	1
second.	1
At	1
seventy	1
or	1
