iron	1
would	1
do.	1
But	1
a	1
very	1
interesting	1
recent	1
research	1
shows	1
that	1
there	1
are	1
two	1
kinds	1
of	1
red	1
stars;	1
some	1
of	1
them	1
are	1
amongst	1
the	1
oldest	1
stars	1
and	1
some	1
are	1
amongst	1
the	1
youngest.	1
The	1
facts	1
appear	1
to	1
be	1
that	1
when	1
a	1
star	1
is	1
first	1
formed	1
it	1
is	1
not	1
very	1
hot.	1
It	1
is	1
an	1
immense	1
mass	1
of	1
diffuse	1
gas	1
glowing	1
with	1
a	1
dull-red	1
heat.	1
It	1
contracts	1
under	1
the	1
mutual	1
gravitation	1
of	1
its	1
particles,	1
and	1
as	1
it	1
does	1
so	1
it	1
grows	1
hotter.	1
It	1
acquires	1
