have	1
said,	1
some	1
eminent	1
astronomers	1
hold	1
that	1
the	1
spiral	1
nebulære	1
universes	1
like	1
our	1
own,	1
and	1
if	1
we	1
look	1
at	1
the	1
two	1
photographs	1
(Figs.	1
25	1
and	1
26)	1
