very	1
remarkable.	1
The	1
nebula	1
in	1
Coma	1
Berenices	1
is	1
a	1
spiral	1
edge-on	1
to	1
us,	1
and	1
we	1
see	1
that	1
it	1
has	1
precisely	1
the	1
lens-shaped	1
middle	1
and	1
the	1
general	1
flattened	1
shape	1
that	1
we	1
have	1
found	1
in	1
our	1
own	1
system.	1
The	1
nebula	1
in	1
Canes	1
Venatici	1
is	1
a	1
spiral	1
facing	1
towards	1
us,	1
and	1
