shape	1
irresistibly	1
suggests	1
motions	1
along	1
the	1
spiral	1
arms.	1
This	1
motion,	1
whether	1
it	1
is	1
towards	1
or	1
away	1
from	1
the	1
central,	1
lens-shaped	1
portion,	1
would	1
cause	1
a	1
double	1
streaming	1
motion	1
in	1
that	1
central	1
portion	1
of	1
the	1
kind	1
we	1
have	1
found	1
in	1
our	1
own	1
system.	1
Again,	1
and	1
altogether	1
apart	1
from	1
these	1
considerations,	1
there	1
are	1
good	1
reasons	1
for	1
supposing	1
our	1
