Way	1
(see	1
Fig.	1
22)	1
would	1
give	1
very	1
much	1
the	1
mottled	1
appearance	1
we	1
notice	1
in	1
the	1
arms	1
(which	1
we	1
see	1
edge-on)	1
of	1
the	1
nebula	1
in	1
Coma	1
Berenices.	1
The	1
hypothesis,	1
therefore,	1
that	1
our	1
universe	1
is	1
a	1
spiral	1
nebula	1
has	1
much	1
to	1
be	1
said	1
for	1
it.	1
If	1
it	1
be	1
accepted	1
it	1
greatly	1
increases	1
our	1
estimate	1
of	1
the	1
size	1
of	1
the	1
material	1
universe.	1
For	1
our	1
central,	1
lens-shaped	1
system	1
is	1
calculated	1
to	1
extend	1
towards	1
the	1
Milky	1
Way	1
for	1
more	1
than	1
twenty	1
