and	1
without	1
the	1
same	1
facility	1
of	1
movement,	1
but	1
which,	1
by	1
a	1
number	1
of	1
exquisite	1
refinements,	1
are	1
more	1
adapted	1
to	1
accurate	1
measurements.	1
It	1
is	1
these	1
instruments	1
which	1
are	1
chiefly	1
used	1
in	1
the	1
compilation	1
of	1
the	1
_Nautical	1
Almanac_.	1
They	1
do	1
not	1
follow	1
the	1
apparent	1
motions	1
of	1
the	1
stars.	1
Stars	1
are	1
allowed	1
to	1
drift	1
across	1
the	1
field	1
of	1
vision,	1
and	1
as	1
each	1
star	1
crosses	1
a	1
small	1
group	1
of	1
parallel	1
wires	1
in	1
the	1
