split	1
up	1
light	1
falling	1
on	1
them	1
into	1
its	1
constituents	1
and	1
produce	1
a	1
spectrum.	1
The	1
modern	1
diffraction	1
grating	1
is	1
a	1
truly	1
wonderful	1
piece	1
of	1
work.	1
It	1
contains	1
several	1
thousands	1
of	1
lines	1
to	1
the	1
inch,	1
and	1
these	1
lines	1
have	1
to	1
