spaced	1
with	1
the	1
greatest	1
accuracy.	1
But	1
in	1
this	1
instrument,	1
again,	1
there	1
is	1
a	1
considerable	1
loss	1
of	1
light.	1
We	1
have	1
said	1
that	1
every	1
substance	1
has	1
its	1
own	1
distinctive	1
spectrum,	1
and	1
it	1
might	1
be	1
thought	1
that,	1
when	1
a	1
