The	1
Beginning	1
of	1
Sexual	1
Reproduction	1
A	1
freshwater	1
Hydra,	1
growing	1
on	1
the	1
duckweed	1
usually	1
multiplies	1
by	1
budding.	1
It	1
forms	1
