living	1
images	1
of	1
itself;	1
a	1
check	1
comes	1
to	1
nutrition	1
and	1
these	1
daughter-buds	1
go	1
free.	1
A	1
big	1
sea-anemone	1
may	1
divide	1
in	1
two	1
or	1
more	1
parts,	1
which	1
become	1
separate	1
animals.	1
This	1
is	1
