rise	1
to	1
the	1
egg-cells	1
and	1
the	1
sperm-cells.	1
The	1
advantages	1
of	1
this	1
method	1
are	1
great.	1
(1)	1
The	1
new	1
generation	1
is	1
started	1
less	1
expensively,	1
for	1
it	1
is	1
easier	1
to	1
shed	1
