separate	1
off	1
half	1
of	1
the	1
body.	1
(2)	1
It	1
is	1
possible	1
to	1
start	1
a	1
great	1
many	1
new	1
lives	1
at	1
once,	1
and	1
this	1
may	1
be	1
of	1
vital	1
importance	1
when	1
the	1
struggle	1
for	1
existence	1
is	1
very	1
keen,	1
and	1
when	1
parental	1
care	1
is	1
impossible.	1
(3)	1
