dints	1
impressed	1
on	1
the	1
body	1
of	1
the	1
parent--little	1
likely	1
unless	1
the	1
dints	1
have	1
peculiarly	1
penetrating	1
consequences,	1
as	1
in	1
the	1
case	1
of	1
poisons.	1
(4)	1
A	1
further	1
advantage	1
is	1
implied	1
in	1
the	1
formation	1
of	1
two	1
kinds	1
of	1
germ-cells--the	1
