The	1
Beginning	1
of	1
Natural	1
Death	1
There	1
are	1
three	1
chief	1
kinds	1
of	1
death,	1
(_a_)	1
The	1
great	1
majority	1
of	1
animals	1
come	1
to	1
a	1
violent	1
end,	1
being	1
devoured	1
by	1
others	1
or	1
killed	1
by	1
sudden	1
and	1
extreme	1
changes	1
in	1
their	1
surroundings.	1
(_b_)	1
When	1
an	1
animal	1
enters	1
a	1
new	1
habitat,	1
or	1
comes	1
into	1
new	1
