to	1
change;	1
perhaps	1
because	1
it	1
is	1
the	1
vehicle	1
of	1
a	1
multitude	1
of	1
hereditary	1
items	1
among	1
which	1
there	1
are	1
very	1
likely	1
to	1
be	1
reshufflings	1
or	1
rearrangements;	1
perhaps	1
because	1
the	1
germ-cells	1
have	1
very	1
changeful	1
surroundings	1
(the	1
blood,	1
the	1
body-cavity	1
fluid,	1
the	1
sea-water);	1
perhaps	1
because	1
deeply	1
saturating	1
outside	1
