I.	1
THE	1
SHORE	1
OF	1
THE	1
SEA	1
The	1
Seaweed	1
Area	1
By	1
the	1
shore	1
of	1
the	1
sea	1
the	1
zoologist	1
means	1
much	1
more	1
than	1
the	1
narrow	1
zone	1
between	1
