feeds.	1
An	1
index	1
of	1
the	1
intensity	1
of	1
the	1
struggle	1
for	1
food	1
is	1
afforded	1
by	1
the	1
nutritive	1
chains	1
which	1
bind	1
animals	1
together.	1
The	1
shore	1
is	1
almost	1
noisy	1
with	1
the	1
conjugation	1
of	1
the	1
verb	1
to	1
eat	1
in	1
its	1
