struggle	1
for	1
existence	1
in	1
the	1
frequency	1
of	1
"shifts	1
for	1
a	1
living,"	1
adaptations	1
of	1
structure	1
or	1
of	1
behaviour	1
which	1
meet	1
frequently	1
recurrent	1
vicissitudes.	1
The	1
starfish	1
is	1
often	1
in	1
the	1
