preformed	1
bandage	1
which	1
prevents	1
bleeding	1
a	1
new	1
leg	1
is	1
formed	1
in	1
miniature.	1
Such	1
is	1
the	1
adaptive	1
device--more	1
reflex	1
than	1
reflective--which	1
is	1
called	1
self-mutilation	1
or	1
autotomy.	1
In	1
another	1
part	1
of	1
this	1
book	1
there	1
is	1
a	1
discussion	1
of	1
camouflaging	1
and	1
protective	1
