how	1
abundantly	1
these	1
are	1
illustrated	1
on	1
the	1
shore!	1
But	1
there	1
are	1
other	1
"shifts	1
for	1
a	1
living."	1
Some	1
of	1
the	1
sand-hoppers	1
and	1
their	1
relatives	1
