of	1
absolute	1
calm	1
and	1
silence,	1
and	1
there	1
is	1
no	1
scenery	1
on	1
the	1
floor.	1
A	1
deep,	1
cold,	1
dark,	1
silent,	1
monotonous	1
world!	1
Biological	1
Conditions	1
While	1
some	1
parts	1
of	1
the	1
floor	1
of	1
the	1
abysses	1
are	1
more	1
thickly	1
peopled	1
than	1
others,	1
