representing	1
nude	1
female	1
figures	1
are	1
also	1
known.	1
The	1
elaborate	1
burial	1
customs	1
point	1
to	1
a	1
belief	1
in	1
life	1
after	1
death.	1
They	1
made	1
stone	1
implements--knives,	1
