gravers,	1
and	1
the	1
like,	1
of	1
the	1
type	1
known	1
as	1
Palæithic,	1
and	1
these	1
show	1
interesting	1
gradations	1
of	1
skill	1
and	1
peculiarities	1
of	1
style.	1
The	1
"Cave-men"	1
lived	1
between	1
the	1
third	1
and	1
fourth	1
Ice	1
Ages,	1
along	1
with	1
cave-bear,	1
