body,	1
clearness	1
and	1
alertness	1
of	1
mind,	1
and	1
an	1
indispensable	1
sociality.	1
The	1
most	1
powerful	1
factors	1
in	1
the	1
world	1
are	1
clear	1
ideas	1
in	1
the	1
minds	1
of	1
energetic	1
men	1
of	1
good	1
will.	1
The	1
differences	1
in	1
bodily	1
and	1
mental	1
health	1
which	1
mark	1
races,	1
and	1
stocks	1
within	1
a	1
people,	1
just	1
as	1
they	1
mark	1
