and	1
to	1
the	1
kind	1
of	1
sifting	1
to	1
which	1
the	1
race	1
or	1
stock	1
has	1
been	1
subjected.	1
Easygoing	1
conditions	1
are	1
not	1
only	1
without	1
stimulus	1
to	1
new	1
departures,	1
they	1
are	1
without	1
the	1
sifting	1
which	1
progress	1
demands.	1
As	1
to	1
PLACE,	1
it	1
is	1
plain	1
that	1
different	1
areas	1
differ	1
