will	1
not	1
make	1
for	1
much	1
progress	1
unless	1
the	1
climate	1
is	1
such	1
that	1
they	1
can	1
be	1
readily	1
utilised.	1
Indeed,	1
climate	1
has	1
been	1
one	1
of	1
the	1
great	1
factors	1
in	1
civilisation,	1
here	1
stimulating	1
and	1
there	1
depressing	1
energy,	1
in	1
one	1
place	1
favouring	1
certain	1
plants	1
and	1
animals	1
important	1
to	1
man,	1
in	1
another	1
place	1
preventing	1
their	1
presence.	1
Moreover,	1
climate	1
has	1
slowly	1
changed	1
from	1
age	1
to	1
age.	1
As	1
to	1
WORK,	1
the	1
form	1
of	1
a	1
civilisation	1
is	1
in	1
some	1
