protruding	1
bag	1
of	1
yolk	1
has	1
disappeared	1
and	1
the	1
_fry_,	1
about	1
an	1
inch	1
long,	1
begin	1
to	1
move	1
about	1
more	1
actively	1
and	1
to	1
fend	1
for	1
themselves.	1
By	1
the	1
end	1
of	1
the	1
year	1
