life.	1
To	1
most	1
of	1
us	1
this	1
theory	1
is	1
impossible,	1
because	1
we	1
are	1
quite	1
sure	1
that	1
ideas	1
and	1
feelings	1
and	1
purposes,	1
which	1
cannot	1
be	1
translated	1
into	1
matter	1
and	1
motion,	1
are	1
the	1
