of	1
round,	1
smooth	1
atoms,	1
which	1
would	1
not	1
cling	1
together.	1
Then	1
there	1
were	1
atoms	1
with	1
rough	1
surfaces,	1
"hooky"	1
surfaces,	1
and	1
these	1
stuck	1
together	1
and	1
formed	1
solids.	1
The	1
atoms	1
of	1
iron	1
or	1
