are	1
not	1
indivisible.	1
They	1
consist	1
themselves	1
of	1
still	1
smaller	1
particles,	1
as	1
we	1
shall	1
see.	1
But	1
the	1
atoms	1
exist	1
all	1
the	1
same,	1
and	1
we	1
may	1
still	1
say	1
that	1
they	1
are	1
the	1
bricks	1
of	1
which	1
the	1
material	1
universe	1
is	1
built.	1
[Illustration:	1
_Photo:	1
Elliott	1
&	1
Fry._	1
SIR	1
ERNEST	1
RUTHERFORD	1
One	1
of	1
our	1
most	1
eminent	1
