[Illustration:	1
_Photo:	1
Rischgitz	1
Collection._	1
J.	1
CLERK-MAXWELL	1
One	1
of	1
the	1
greatest	1
scientific	1
men	1
who	1
have	1
ever	1
lived.	1
He	1
revolutionised	1
physics	1
with	1
his	1
electro-magnetic	1
theory	1
of	1
light,	1
and	1
practically	1
all	1
modern	1
researches	1
have	1
had	1
