century.]	1
[Illustration:	1
_Photo:	1
Ernest	1
H.	1
Mills._	1
SIR	1
WILLIAM	1
CROOKES	1
Sir	1
William	1
Crookes	1
experimented	1
on	1
the	1
electric	1
discharge	1
in	1
vacuum	1
tubes	1
and	1
described	1
