of	1
colour.	1
Here	1
and	1
there	1
is	1
a	1
black	1
patch,	1
which	1
_absorbs_	1
all	1
the	1
light.	1
White	1
surfaces	1
_reflect_	1
the	1
whole	1
of	1
it.	1
What	1
is	1
reflected	1
depends	1
on	1
the	1
period	1
of	1
vibration	1
of	1
the	1
electrons	1
in	1
the	1
