ENERGY:	1
HOW	1
ALL	1
LIFE	1
DEPENDS	1
ON	1
IT	1
As	1
we	1
have	1
seen	1
in	1
an	1
earlier	1
chapter,	1
one	1
of	1
the	1
fundamental	1
entities	1
of	1
the	1
universe	1
is	1
matter.	1
A	1
second,	1
not	1
less	1
important,	1
is	1
called	1
energy.	1
Energy	1
is	1
indispensable	1
if	1
the	1
world	1
is	1
to	1
continue	1
to	1
exist,	1
since	1
all	1
phenomena,	1
including	1
life,	1
depend	1
on	1
it.	1
Just	1
as	1
it	1
is	1
humanly	1
impossible	1
to	1
create	1
or	1
to	1
destroy	1
a	1
particle	1
of	1
matter,	1
so	1
is	1
it	1
impossible	1
to	1
create	1
or	1
to	1
destroy	1
energy.	1
This	1
