thirty	1
years,	1
he	1
produced	1
and	1
distributed	1
Project	1
Gutenberg-tm	1
eBooks	1
with	1
only	1
a	1
loose	1
network	1
of	1
volunteer	1
support.	1
Project	1
Gutenberg-tm	1
eBooks	1
are	1
often	1
created	1
from	1
several	1
printed	1
editions,	1
all	1
of	1
which	1
are	1
confirmed	1
as	1
Public	1
Domain	1
in	1
the	1
U.S.	1
unless	1
a	1
copyright	1
notice	1
is	1
included.	1
Thus,	1
we	1
do	1
not	1
necessarily	1
keep	1
eBooks	1
in	1
compliance	1
with	1
any	1
particular	1
paper	1
edition.	1
